# BGIN AI Block 14 Frontend Rebuild ‚Äî Coding Agent Package

## What This Is

Documentation package for rebuilding the BGIN AI frontend aligned with the agentprivacy "Three Graphs, One Identity" architecture. Read ALL files before writing code.

