## Three Graphs Model

```
KNOWLEDGE GRAPH (Substrate)
    ‚Üì what you engage with
PROMISE GRAPH (Overlay)
    ‚Üì what you commit to
TRUST GRAPH (Emergent)
    ‚Üì what you've proven

Unique intersection = participant identity
```

## The Duality

- **Swordsman ‚öîÔ∏è** ‚Äî Generated at key ceremony. Client-side. Guards privacy boundaries. Enforces Chatham House cryptographically.
- **Mage üßô** ‚Äî One per working group, shared. Server-side RAG. Navigates collective knowledge. Never sees what Swordsman hides.

The gap between them is where governance happens.

